能，而這部分的實作就當作我出給你的最終作業囉。",[16,833,834,835],{},"今天這一份程式碼將會放在這個儲存庫：",[70,836,837],{"href":837,"rel":838},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fjavascript-to-python",[74],[12,840,841],{"id":841},"作者的話",[16,843,844],{},"前陣子朋友問了我一下如何入門投資與創造被動收入，後來我想了一下就將之前自己的一些小小心得寫成了一篇文章分享給他，雖然不知道對他是否有幫助，但是最主要期望他在思考這問題之前先解決自己金錢上管控的問題，畢竟他真的不太會控管自己金流 QQ",[16,846,847],{},"如果有興趣的人也可以參考看看（？）",[16,849,850],{},[70,851,853],{"href":852},"\u002Flearnexp\u002F20210710\u002F1926104502\u002F","創造被動收入之前的準備與理財入門",[12,855,856],{"id":856},"關於兔兔們",[29,858,859,866,874,882],{},[32,860,861],{},[70,862,865],{"href":863,"rel":864},"https:\u002F\u002Ftailwindcss.tw",[74],"Tailwind CSS 臺灣官網",[32,867,868,873],{},[70,869,872],{"href":870,"rel":871},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Ftailwindcss.tw",[74],"Tailwind CSS 臺灣"," (臉書粉絲專頁)",[32,875,876,881],{},[70,877,880],{"href":878,"rel":879},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Fgroups\u002Ftailwindcss.taiwan",[74],"兔兔教 × Tailwind CSS Taiwan"," (臉書社群)",[32,883,884],{},[70,885,888],{"href":886,"rel":887},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Flalarabbits-%E5%85%94%E5%85%94%E6%95%99%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%AC%E7%87%9F-102150975410839\u002F",[74],"兔兔教大本營",[16,890,891],{},[191,892],{"alt":893,"src":894},"兔法無邊","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FPwE2UE9.jpg",[896,897,898],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}",{"title":93,"searchDepth":132,"depth":132,"links":900},[901,902,903,90